{{codepointer|Sound}}'''A_XScream'''
(no parameters)
Plays the {{c|*gibbed}} [[Player sounds|player sound]] if called by a player, otherwise it plays {{c|misc/gibbed}}. The sound is played on the ''voice'' [[Sound channels|channel]].
== Examples == XDeath: POSS M 5 POSS N 5 '''A_XScream''' POSS O 5 [[A_NoBlocking]] POSS PQRST 5 POSS U -1 stop This is the XDeath state for ''[[Doom]]'''s {{Class|ZombieMan}}
